@DoctorAppointment.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5229

### ==================== CHATBOT TESTS ====================

### Test 1: Guest Chat (No Auth Required) - Test Basic Symptom
POST {{DoctorAppointment.API_HostAddress}}/api/medai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I have a headache and mild fever for 2 days. What should I do?"
}

###

### Test 2: Guest Chat - Emergency Test
POST {{DoctorAppointment.API_HostAddress}}/api/medai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I'm having chest pain and difficulty breathing"
}

###

### Test 3: Guest Chat - General Health Question
POST {{DoctorAppointment.API_HostAddress}}/api/medai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What are good habits for maintaining a healthy lifestyle?"
}

###
